snippet.title: DRAGON QUEST MONSTERS: The Dark Prince Steam & Mobile Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
DRAGON QUEST MONSTERS: The Dark Prince is coming to Steam ® and Mobile on September 11, 2024.

Get ready to embark on a journey for revenge. Join Psaro, a cursed demon prince, as he scouts, combines, and creates legions of monsters to take into battle on his path to becoming the Master of Monsterkind.

Follow us to stay up to date with the latest DRAGON QUEST MONSTERS: The Dark Prince news:
Website: https://dragonquestmonsters.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/dragonquest
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/dragonquest/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DragonQuest/
